title: Breaking Down ‘Selling Sunset’ Season 4 With David Jacoby
description:
Juliet is joined by ESPN broadcaster and longtime friend David Jacoby to break down Season 4 of ‘Selling Sunset.’ They examine which drama was real and which was fake, discuss their mixed feelings about Christine, and review celebrity cameos from this season. 
Host: Juliet Litman
Guest: David Jacoby
Producer: Devon Manze
